*** UNIX VERSION ***

DEPENDENCIES

libtiff for TIFF support
libjpeg for JPEG support
libpng for PNG support

INSTALLATION

./configure
make
make install

You will also need to manually copy the man pages to the relevant location.

*** WINDOWS VERSION ***

Just use the DLL inside the Debug folder, or run setup.exe from activex/

